# Regression (#517, negative + DEFERRED case): a raw collection is not (yet) iterable. `loop mut x
# in xs` over a `[]i64` desugars to a closure-call `_it()`; a slice is not callable, so it fails
# typing — the documented deferred case (raw-collection for-each needs IntoIterator). No build.
name = "loop_foreach_raw_collection"
